# Waste Classification Dataset

This folder contains a **small sample** of the full dataset used in the project for demonstration purposes.

The full dataset can be downloaded from Kaggle:  
[Waste Classification Dataset by techsash](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/techsash/waste-classification-data)

### Structure of the sample dataset:

- `dataset_sample/TRAIN/organic/` : Sample organic waste images for training
- `dataset_sample/TRAIN/recyclable/` : Sample recyclable waste images for training
- `dataset_sample/TEST/organic/` : Sample organic waste images for testing
- `dataset_sample/TEST/recyclable/` : Sample recyclable waste images for testing

> ⚠️ Note: This is only a subset of the original dataset. To run full training, download the complete dataset from the Kaggle link above.
